data.text:
Park City, UT, USA

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 40.646061, -111.497971.

Park City is a very small town in Utah, a known tourist spot and a settlement with a wonderful location, in a small valley between the mountains. It is a very popular venue for various cinema and arts festivals, exhibitions and movie filming activities. There are three ski resorts, numerous sports clubs and other excellent modern recreation facilities. Park City can be an excellent vacation spot.
